Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: 3,152 sq. ft. of office available for lease. 1.5 km from 401 with 4.5 acres of yard available for lease. Located in Puslinch, ON at Exit 299 off of the 401, 15 min to Milton. Building offers in floor heating in the shop area and fully functional pits. CTPAT yard. Building is fully furnished complete with IT, phone system, office furniture and security system (22 cameras). Multiple options available including leasing the building and entire yard or multiple configurations of outdoor storage area. Both long and short term options available.

Brand New 40,500 Sq. Ft. Office Development Ready For Q3 2022. Unit 1 24,300 Sq. Ft. Available. Unit 2 16,200 Sq. Ft. Leased. Located In Prestigious Hanlon Creek Business Park. Corporate Setting Surrounded By Green Space, Recreational Trails And Many Brand New Developments. Reputable First-Class Commercial Developer. Includes $40 TIA and a finished office shell.

4,392 SF of professionally finished office space located in University of Guelph's Research Park. Conveniently located within close proximity to the University of Guelph, Stone Road Mall, fitness centers, restaurants and plenty more amenities. Easy access to Hwy 6 Hanlon Pkwy as well as Highway 401. The building offers ample parking, plenty of natural light and recently renovated common areas

A New 200-Year-Old Leasing Opportunity. The Heritage Building at 43 Arthur Street has been standing on the banks of the Speed River since 1827 and for 200 years its occupants have helped shape Guelph. Its time for a new generation of visionaries to carry the torch. Office space and retail space available now. A variety of sizes and configurations available. Beautiful brick and beam space in the heart of Guelph close to amenities, trails, parking and more.
